      <event start="T277" end="T759-233">to ni nekaj za imeti. </event>
      <event start="T759-233" end="T119">Ampak čakaj, </event>
      <event start="T119" end="T278">to ima tudi M chipe not, </event>
      <event start="T278" end="T761-51">a ne? </event>
      <event start="T764-464" end="T765-474">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T777-532" end="T779-016">Pa dobro. </event>
      <event start="T779-016" end="T783-37">[smeh] Kaj boš pa tam delal, da rabiš več kot M1? </event>
      <event start="T785-304" end="T280">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T280" end="T121">in? </event>
      <event start="T121" end="T122">Se pozna? </event>
      <event start="T122" end="T788-352">Da je p() star? </event>
      <event start="T790-618" end="T792-928">Mmm. </event>
      <event start="T802-114" end="T283">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T283" end="T803-533">to pa je ja ja. </event>
      <event start="T803-533" end="T804-445">Tipi() ... </event>
      <event start="T805-308" end="T806-161">Tipičen </event>
      <event start="T806-161" end="T284">eem </event>
      <event start="T284" end="T808-666">Apple zadev. </event>
      <event start="T808-666" end="T123">Tudi OLED zaslona nimajo nikjer. </event>
      <event start="T123" end="T124">Ali imajo? </event>
      <event start="T124" end="T125">Imajo na Projih, </event>
      <event start="T125" end="T813-603">a ne? </event>
      <event start="T823-186" end="T826-071">Zakaj bi to pol kupil? </event>
      <event start="T826-071" end="T828-211">OLED je kar dobro. </event>
      <event start="T828-211" end="T830-589">Moj laptop ima OLED. </event>
      <event start="T830-589" end="T832-847">Mi je kar všeč. </event>
      <event start="T832-847" end="T838-091">Sicer ga imam večino na šestdeset hercev. [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T838-091" end="T839-395">Malo baterije prišpara. </event>
      <event start="T839-395" end="T842-411">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T844-887" end="T288">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T288" end="T129">če je priklopljen pa kaj i() igram, </event>
      <event start="T129" end="T289">pol eee dvesto štirideset, </event>
      <event start="T289" end="T850-645">a ne? </event>
      <event start="T851-105" end="T851-977">Če je pa </event>
      <event start="T851-977" end="T130">če pa na bateriji, da berem nek članek za faks, </event>
      <event start="T130" end="T858-052">pol pa ne rabim, da je sto štirideset eee ... </event>
      <event start="T860-719" end="T131">Ja ja, </event>
      <event start="T131" end="T864-561">ful jaz scrollam tako hitro, da to nujno rabim. </event>
      <event start="T864-561" end="T290">Saj veš, </event>
      <event start="T290" end="T132">da če samo dosti počasi scrollaš, </event>
      <event start="T132" end="T291">pol ne opaziš, </event>
      <event start="T291" end="T868-558">a ne? [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T869-779" end="T133">[smeh] Ja. </event>
      <event start="T133" end="T293">Tako da ne, </event>
      <event start="T293" end="T875-636">ne morem reči, da pogrešam pri scrollanju. [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T875-636" end="T134">Pa itak je OLED. </event>
      <event start="T134" end="T878-913">Pri OLEDU je to malo drugače. </event>
      <event start="T878-913" end="T884-315">Tam je tudi šestdeset herc malo boljše k na IPS-u ali pa kaj takega. </event>
      <event start="T886-09" end="T889-203">K se piksli hitreje refreshajo. </event>
      <event start="T889-203" end="T893-247">Že tako pač tisti black to black response rate imajo ful hitro. </event>
      <event start="T893-247" end="T895-296">In eem ... </event>
      <event start="T898-419" end="T294">Pač hitreje lahko grejo iz svetlega na temno nazaj na svetlo, </event>
      <event start="T294" end="T135">a ne, </event>
      <event start="T135" end="T295">in pol je vse malo bolj čisto, ko se spreminjajo zadeve, </event>
      <event start="T295" end="T906-781">a ne? </event>
      <event start="T906-781" end="T296">Ni nič zamazan, </event>
      <event start="T296" end="T136">tako. </event>
      <event start="T136" end="T911-258">Nimaš tistega ghostinga, k bi ga imel ... </event>
      <event start="T911-258" end="T913-002">na več. </event>
      <event start="T913-002" end="T297">Je še zmeraj malo, </event>
      <event start="T297" end="T915-302">ni ga toliko. </event>
      <event start="T915-302" end="T137">In pol jaz </event>
      <event start="T137" end="T197">pol je tudi pri šestdeset hercih malo boljše ssš slika. </event>
      <event start="T197" end="T921-575">Ni tako opazno. </event>
      <event start="T925-966" end="T298">Ja to je pa pač samo ... </event>
      <event start="T298" end="T299">ena stopnja med OLEDOM pa IPS-om, </event>
      <event start="T299" end="T138">namesto da je vsak piksel ena lučka, je, </event>
      <event start="T138" end="T139">ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T139" end="T936-619">dva tisoč lučk. </event>
      <event start="T936-619" end="T938-728">In pol so na cone razdeljene. </event>
      <event start="T938-728" end="T940-612">Pippppp. </event>
      <event start="T940-612" end="T300">In ja eem </event>
      <event start="T300" end="T947-944">in pol imaš malo tako, best of both worlds zadevo recimo. </event>
      <event start="T947-944" end="T363">K lahko še zmeraj ugasne, </event>
      <event start="T363" end="T301">tiste, k so na črnem, </event>
      <event start="T301" end="T303">k so čisto na črnem, </event>
      <event start="T303" end="T302">a ne, </event>
      <event start="T302" end="T954-423">tiste vseeno ugasnejo. </event>
      <event start="T954-423" end="T960-34">Sicer imaš lahko pol okrog kakšnih svetlih objektov tako malo tak halo okoli. </event>
      <event start="T961-184" end="T140">Malo se vidi. </event>
      <event start="T140" end="T163">To je, </event>
      <event start="T163" end="T305">čeprav to je bolj na televizijah, </event>
      <event start="T305" end="T966-784">ne vem, koliko bi to na takem majhnem zaslonu opazili. </event>
      <event start="T968-203" end="T164">Eee je pač, </event>
      <event start="T164" end="T973-062">ne vem, koliko imajo teh zdaj ledic noter. </event>
      <event start="T973-062" end="T307">K z() </event>
      <event start="T307" end="T308">to še zmeraj jih razporediš na dosti majhno površino, </event>
      <event start="T308" end="T142">a ne, </event>
      <event start="T142" end="T141">in če je dosti majhna lučka, </event>
      <event start="T141" end="T309">jah, </event>
      <event start="T309" end="T310">to, da to ne boš glih videl, </event>
      <event start="T310" end="T981-325">a ne. </event>
      <event start="T981-325" end="T311">Eem </event>
      <event start="T311" end="T986-288">prednost pred OLED je pa res, da [nerazumljivo] ne morejo obrniti in. </event>
      <event start="T986-288" end="T988-775">Aam pa svetlejši so. </event>
      <event start="T988-775" end="T312">Tako da za zunaj boljše, </event>
      <event start="T312" end="T992-56">I guess? </event>
      <event start="T994-883" end="T996-077">Ehm. </event>
      <event start="T1007-497" end="T144">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T144" end="T1009-583">to bi bilo kar fajn. </event>
      <event start="T1009-583" end="T317">Bz() z() </event>
      <event start="T317" end="T1012-542">zelo dobra tehnologija. </event>
      <event start="T1012-542" end="T1014-266">To je kar prihodnost. </event>
      <event start="T1014-266" end="T1015-494">Čudno, da so toliko cajta ... </event>
      <event start="T1015-494" end="T1016-168">[nerazumljivo] </event>
      <event start="T1018-458" end="T318">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T318" end="T1020-214">ampak ne() not the best. </event>
      <event start="T1020-214" end="T1024-446">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1024-446" end="T145">Ja glej. </event>
      <event start="T145" end="T146">Pač to je tak eem </event>
      <event start="T146" end="T319">eee </event>
      <event start="T319" end="T320">tak vmesni korak, </event>
      <event start="T320" end="T321">a ne, </event>
      <event start="T321" end="T1031-525">bomo rekli. </event>
      <event start="T1031-525" end="T322">Dokler o() ne pogruntajo, da je OLED lahko še svetel pa ne </event>
      <event start="T322" end="T323">nnn se ne zažge, </event>
      <event start="T323" end="T1037-734">a ne. </event>
      <event start="T1047-237" end="T148">Možno. </event>
      <event start="T148" end="T1049-409">Ne vem. </event>
      <event start="T1050-748" end="T1052-464">Ampak ja. </event>
      <event start="T1056-201" end="T326">Ja ampak kkk </event>
      <event start="T326" end="T150">ne vem, kako točno, </event>
      <event start="T150" end="T151">k k same ledice s() ne gre svetloba čez, </event>
      <event start="T151" end="T1065-427">tako da imaš samo ena plast, k zakriva ta spodnjo plast. </event>
      <event start="T1065-427" end="T1069-751">To to s() to mi neki ne tulele neki ne štima. </event>
      <event start="T1070-813" end="T328">Eem. </event>
      <event start="T328" end="T1073-282">Ampak ja. </event>
      <event start="T1073-282" end="T1078-989">Zato se tudi pol zdaj pri televizijah ful pojavlja, k so OLEDI malo bolj temni. </event>
      <event start="T1078-989" end="T1082-078">In pol če ga daš v neko sončno dnevno sobo, </event>
      <event start="T1082-078" end="T329">eem </event>
      <event start="T329" end="T152">ne vidiš kaj dosti. </event>
      <event start="T152" end="T330">Lahko če glih gor sonce posije, </event>
      <event start="T330" end="T1089-233">ga magari ugasneš. </event>
      <event start="T1091-016" end="T1093-571">Tako ja. </event>
      <event start="T1093-571" end="T1095-328">[zvok] </event>
      <event start="T1095-328" end="T1096-662">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1098-364" end="T1099-664">Kaj pa zdaj? </event>
      <event start="T1111-208" end="T1113-162">Ja zdaj je nine a prišel. </event>
      <event start="T1118-841" end="T1121-726">Pol pa deset a() ali nekaj. [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1123-422" end="T1124-516">Ja ne vem, kaj bodo naredili. </event>
      <event start="T1133-92" end="T1136-647">Mh, v primerjavi s katerim? </event>
      <event start="T1138-72" end="T154">Aja, </event>
      <event start="T154" end="T153">ne vem. </event>
      <event start="T153" end="T1141-442">Kamera najbrž. </event>
      <event start="T1141-442" end="T155">A je malo manjši? </event>
      <event start="T155" end="T1144-696">Prr. Ne vem. </event>
      <event start="T1146-016" end="T156">V živo? </event>
      <event start="T156" end="T1147-355">Ne. </event>
      <event start="T1148-873" end="T157">Aja, </event>
      <event start="T157" end="T331">ja, </event>
      <event start="T331" end="T332">zdaj imajo drugo kamero, </event>
      <event start="T332" end="T158">ja. </event>
      <event start="T158" end="T1153-046">Tako čudno je. </event>
      <event start="T1155-693" end="T1156-524">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1156-524" end="T1158-023">Ja malo debelejši je. </event>
      <event start="T1162-81" end="T1164-189">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1172-523" end="T1173-862">Tja. </event>
      <event start="T1178-847" end="T333">No, </event>
      <event start="T333" end="T1180-88">meni se nič ne skrije. [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1181-844" end="T336">J() ja. [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T336" end="T1185-65">Bre() brez ovitka je še hujše. </event>
      <event start="T1185-65" end="T1187-902">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1191-287" end="T339">Ja ne vem, zakaj je tako velik. [zvok] </event>
      <event start="T339" end="T1193-968">Uuu. </event>
      <event start="T1193-968" end="T340">[smeh] To se po mojem slišalo, </event>
      <event start="T340" end="T1197-572">a? </event>
      <event start="T1199-823" end="T1203-006">[smeh] Ampak eem ja. </event>
      <event start="T1203-006" end="T200">Ja saj ... </event>
      <event start="T200" end="T162">Ja na devet a v bistvu sploh še ni bil do konca pokazan, </event>
      <event start="T162" end="T341">samo kako izgleda, so zaenkrat lahko pokazali, </event>
      <event start="T341" end="T1211-268">a ne? </event>
      <event start="T1211-268" end="T342">Kolikor vem, nisi, </event>
      <event start="T342" end="T1213-655">niso, </event>
      <event start="T1213-655" end="T343">ja, </event>
      <event start="T343" end="T1216-692">niso še mogli vsega pokazati ali nekaj na to foro. </event>
      <event start="T1216-692" end="T1218-623">Ne vem, zakaj. </event>
      <event start="T1225-174" end="T1226-196">Ja? </event>
      <event start="T1241-379" end="T165">Mislim, saj tudi navaden šestnajst je kar nekaj. </event>
      <event start="T165" end="T1246-903">Kdo bo dal toliko denarja za telefon, k ima šestdeset hercev. </event>
      <event start="T1249-495" end="T1250-696">Ja glej. </event>
      <event start="T1252-234" end="T1256-645">Ja to lahko tudi izklopiš na katerem koli telefonu, k ima več hercev. </event>
      <event start="T1256-645" end="T345">Eem </event>
      <event start="T345" end="T201">ne vem no, koliko je? </event>
      <event start="T201" end="T202">Sedemsto, osemsto evrov? </event>
      <event start="T202" end="T1264-016">Jaz pač ne vidim, zakaj bi to nabavljal. </event>
      <event start="T1264-016" end="T1266-553">Šestnajst. </event>
      <event start="T1266-553" end="T1268-831">Pa še OLED ni. </event>
      <event start="T1268-831" end="T166">To je jajc. </event>
      <event start="T166" end="T1272-794">To samo nategujejo. </event>
      <event start="T1276-174" end="T1277-355">A pri e? </event>
      <event start="T1278-992" end="T167">Aja, </event>
      <event start="T167" end="T1281-131">dobro no. </event>
      <event start="T1281-131" end="T168">To je tako k oni, </event>
      <event start="T168" end="T169">kaj je že bil en, </event>
      <event start="T169" end="T170">štiri s ali kateri. </event>
      <event start="T170" end="T346">K če si ga narobe držal, </event>
      <event start="T346" end="T1286-395">ni Wi-Fi lovil. </event>
      <event start="T1286-395" end="T1289-756">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1292-265" end="T171">Dobro, </event>
      <event start="T171" end="T1294-774">to je itak brezveze. </event>
      <event start="T1304-119" end="T1305-37">Ja to naj bi bil ... </event>
      <event start="T1305-984" end="T172">oni Air, a ne? </event>
      <event start="T172" end="T1308-164">Ali kva je že? </event>
      <event start="T1308-164" end="T1309-403">Ali kva? </event>
      <event start="T1309-403" end="T203">Ali Light ali nnn nekaj takega. </event>
      <event start="T203" end="T1311-938">Neko novo ime. </event>
      <event start="T1311-938" end="T1314-386">Za sedemnajst. </event>
      <event start="T1314-386" end="T347">Čeprav se mi zdi, da so razmišljali o tem, </event>
      <event start="T347" end="T1319-983">ampak da ga ne bodo še naredili. </event>
      <event start="T1323-383" end="T173">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T173" end="T1327-516">Pa se mi zdi, da je Air dejansko. </event>
      <event start="T1337-356" end="T174">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T174" end="T1341-576">Pa ne vem, zakva ... </event>
      <event start="T1341-576" end="T175">Ne vem, no. </event>
      <event start="T175" end="T1345-116">Raje imam malo večjo baterijo pa debelejši telefon. </event>
      <event start="T1345-116" end="T1349-376">Pa port. [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1352-935" end="T350">Ja </event>
      <event start="T350" end="T1354-297">ne vem. </event>
      <event start="T1354-297" end="T1356-774">[premor] </event>
      <event start="T1356-774" end="T176">I guess. </event>
      <event start="T176" end="T1360-935">Ma ne vem. </event>
      <event start="T1362-733" end="T1364-191">MagSafe? </event>
      <event start="T1371-641" end="T177">Pa to se samo nekaj greje. </event>
      <event start="T177" end="T1375-089">To je brezveze. </event>
      <event start="T1376-516" end="T1377-725">Kaj? </event>
    </tier>
    <tier id="COLLOQ_ROG-dialog-0014" speaker="ROG-dialog-0014" category="colloq" type="a" display-name="ROG-dialog-0014 [colloq]">
      <event start="T1-682" end="T2-655">Okej. </event>
      <event start="T4-181" end="T2">Pa začnimo. </event>
      <event start="T2" end="T6-67">Drgač, ful dobr. </event>
      <event start="T7-708" end="T8-464">Eem. </event>
      <event start="T8-752" end="T3">Js sem vzel pico. </event>
      <event start="T3" end="T208">Eem </event>
      <event start="T208" end="T4">s s slanino, šunko. </event>
      <event start="T4" end="T15-733">Gor je bla salsa omaka. </event>
      <event start="T15-733" end="T207">Eee </event>
      <event start="T207" end="T364">pa še tko kupčki česna, </event>
      <event start="T364" end="T205">k so bli včasih mal preveč, </event>
      <event start="T205" end="T20-865">ampak ... </event>
      <event start="T20-865" end="T23-06">Drgač kr se lepo ... </event>
      <event start="T24-467" end="T25-872">Kaj pa tvoja? </event>
      <event start="T30-435" end="T32-072">Kero si pa mel? </event>
      <event start="T38-459" end="T40-020">Tist jajc je bil mal preveč pečen, </event>
      <event start="T40-020" end="T40-743">ampak okej. </event>
      <event start="T52-002" end="T53-995">[smeh] Šunka namest salame? </event>
      <event start="T56-011" end="T57-229">[smeh] [nerazumljivo] </event>
      <event start="T58-529" end="T210">Eem. </event>
      <event start="T210" end="T62-088">Kaj m() mojo si vidu? </event>
      <event start="T66-38" end="T12">No dobro, </event>
      <event start="T12" end="T13">sej mam še mal </event>
      <event start="T13" end="T69-483">pa lah probaš pol. </event>
      <event start="T70-545" end="T71-528">Če ti bi ... </event>
      <event start="T73-006" end="T206">Drgač je gor una salsa omaka, </event>
      <event start="T206" end="T14">k js sicer nisem največji ljubitelj. </event>
      <event start="T14" end="T81-717">Pa tut ni() nisem zares vedu, kaj naročam. [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T81-717" end="T354">Eee </event>
      <event start="T354" end="T214">tko da če bi še enkrat naročal, bi tisto dol dal. </event>
      <event start="T214" end="T86-789">Eem ... </event>
      <event start="T90-605" end="T16">Det? </event>
      <event start="T16" end="T17">Če je blo sam tko mej() mejčkn [glas] na vrhu. </event>
      <event start="T17" end="T95-05">Ni blo ... </event>
      <event start="T95-05" end="T18">Pač, </event>
      <event start="T18" end="T19">ime moje pice je bla ... </event>
      <event start="T19" end="T216">eee </event>
      <event start="T216" end="T101-816">domača. </event>
      <event start="T102-502" end="T103-560">Al hišna? </event>
      <event start="T103-976" end="T104-897">[smeh] [nerazumljivo] </event>
      <event start="T104-897" end="T217">Moja hišna, </event>
      <event start="T217" end="T20">okej. </event>
      <event start="T20" end="T21">Moja je bla hišna </event>
      <event start="T21" end="T179">in pač ne vem, kaj je salsa delala na hišni pici, </event>
      <event start="T179" end="T111-364">ampak dobr. </event>
