      <event start="T581-739" end="T582-321">Ja on() ... </event>
      <event start="T584-446" end="T254">Onadva imata sigurno ja, </event>
      <event start="T254" end="T587-628">ampak eem ... </event>
      <event start="T587-628" end="T95">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T95" end="T195">saj ta računalnik bi po moje tudi delal, </event>
      <event start="T195" end="T592-237">če bi ga ves ta čas uporabljal. </event>
      <event start="T595-32" end="T97">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T97" end="T256">zdaj k sem ga, </event>
      <event start="T256" end="T257">veš, </event>
      <event start="T257" end="T99">erasal </event>
      <event start="T99" end="T601-269">pa naložil Base macOS, k pač ni apdejtan. </event>
      <event start="T601-269" end="T604-308">Samo zdaj ga ne spraviš na internet, da bi se apdejtal. </event>
      <event start="T605-918" end="T609-967">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T609-967" end="T259">Saj ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T259" end="T100">no. </event>
      <event start="T100" end="T196">Koga ... </event>
      <event start="T196" end="T615-666">čigava krivda bi to bila, a? </event>
      <event start="T621-88" end="T102">No, </event>
      <event start="T102" end="T261">ampak jaz sem z() e() Apple zagovornik teh novejših naprav, </event>
      <event start="T261" end="T626-251">no. </event>
      <event start="T627-472" end="T103">Zdaj je ta nov. </event>
      <event start="T103" end="T104">Čisto nov, brand new. </event>
      <event start="T104" end="T633-825">Za tisoč sto evrov. </event>
      <event start="T635-323" end="T636-544">M4 Air. </event>
      <event start="T637-765" end="T639-996">Šestnajst giga rama, dvesto petdeset ... </event>
      <event start="T642-544" end="T643-903">Se mi zdi, da. </event>
      <event start="T647-216" end="T649-249">Drugač imajo headphone jacke. </event>
      <event start="T652-451" end="T655-546">Pa dva USB-C-ja. [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T655-546" end="T105">Dva! [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T105" end="T660-096">Točno to dobiš. </event>
      <event start="T665-2" end="T666-936">Kako bi pa več k dva rabil? </event>
      <event start="T668-969" end="T670-249">Miška je Bluetooth. </event>
      <event start="T674-402" end="T677-228">Miško imaš na USB-C priklopljeno? </event>
      <event start="T679-475" end="T681-467">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T685-245" end="T267">Ne, </event>
      <event start="T267" end="T109">pač eem ... </event>
      <event start="T109" end="T268">wireless si, </event>
      <event start="T268" end="T110">a ne. </event>
      <event start="T110" end="T695-164">Saj imaš tudi eee pol AirPods Pro and what not. </event>
      <event start="T699-337" end="T700-328">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T702-147" end="T705-08">Mh. </event>
      <event start="T715-97" end="T112">Nekaj cajta nazaj sem drugače tudi gledal za isto ceno, </event>
      <event start="T112" end="T721-963">pa če imaš zdaj budžet tisoč evrov. </event>
      <event start="T721-963" end="T725-909">Pa pač se ode() osredotočiš na Applov sistem. </event>
      <event start="T725-909" end="T272">Eem. </event>
      <event start="T272" end="T113">MacBook, za jurja. </event>
      <event start="T113" end="T736-253">Ali lahko imaš pa ... iPad Air, Magic Keyboard pa pisalo za jurja. </event>
      <event start="T745-102" end="T746-204">iPad OS. </event>
      <event start="T747-563" end="T748-158">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T750-726" end="T753-314">It's it's a downfall of many. [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T761-51" end="T120">Jap. </event>
      <event start="T120" end="T764-464">The same ones actually. [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T764-464" end="T765-474">Eem ... </event>
      <event start="T765-474" end="T768-794">iPad Air se mi zdi, da je bil zdajle dan ... </event>
      <event start="T768-794" end="T773-064">Zdajle spomladi skupaj s tem eem MacBookom, Airom. </event>
      <event start="T773-064" end="T279">Samo da so iPad Air dali na M3, </event>
      <event start="T279" end="T777-532">ne na M4. </event>
      <event start="T783-37" end="T785-304">Tale ima M2. </event>
      <event start="T787-614" end="T790-618">Tale je iPad Pro M2. </event>
      <event start="T792-928" end="T282">Je pa nekaj, </event>
      <event start="T282" end="T281">kar je malo škoda, da </event>
      <event start="T281" end="T800-5">na nepro zadevah ful prišparajo na refresh ratu. </event>
      <event start="T800-5" end="T802-114">It's only sixty. [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T803-533" end="T805-308">Oziroma pač Air Type Pro. </event>
      <event start="T805-308" end="T806-161">[nerazumljivo] </event>
      <event start="T813-603" end="T285">Tandem OLED, </event>
      <event start="T285" end="T815-253">ja. </event>
      <event start="T815-253" end="T126">Ampak samo na ta novem Proju. </event>
      <event start="T126" end="T819-131">Ta niti ne vem. </event>
      <event start="T819-131" end="T127">Ta dejansko ne vem. </event>
      <event start="T127" end="T823-186">Mogoče ima e() enojen OLED. </event>
      <event start="T839-395" end="T286">Aaa, </event>
      <event start="T286" end="T128">tako. </event>
      <event start="T128" end="T842-411">Vidiš, vidiš, vidiš. </event>
      <event start="T842-411" end="T287">Don't even use the hertz, </event>
      <event start="T287" end="T844-887">eee? [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T850-645" end="T851-105">Ja ... </event>
      <event start="T851-105" end="T851-977">[nerazumljivo] </event>
      <event start="T858-052" end="T860-719">Ampak a nočeš smooth scrolling imeti? </event>
      <event start="T868-558" end="T292">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T292" end="T869-779">that's how it works. [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T884-315" end="T886-09">Zakaj? </event>
      <event start="T895-296" end="T898-419">Da se hitreje ugasnejo, namesto da se počasi už() ugašajo ali kaj? </event>
      <event start="T911-258" end="T913-002">Aha. </event>
      <event start="T921-575" end="T925-966">Kaj pa ta Mini-LED, k ga ima Apple na MacBookih Pro na primer? </event>
      <event start="T960-34" end="T961-184">Mmm. </event>
      <event start="T966-784" end="T306">Ker je ful tanek, </event>
      <event start="T306" end="T968-203">ne? </event>
      <event start="T994-883" end="T313">Je pa zdaj po nekih rumorjih, </event>
      <event start="T313" end="T314">a ne, </event>
      <event start="T314" end="T996-077">da bodo naslednja generacija, </event>
      <event start="T996-077" end="T143">se pravi naslednje leto, </event>
      <event start="T143" end="T1003-760">eem dva šestindvajset, </event>
      <event start="T1003-760" end="T315">MacBooki, </event>
      <event start="T315" end="T316">vsaj Proji, </event>
      <event start="T316" end="T1007-497">na OLED šli. </event>
      <event start="T1012-542" end="T1014-266">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1015-494" end="T1018-458">Ampak si rekel, da je Mini-LED best of both worlds. </event>
      <event start="T1020-214" end="T1024-446">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1037-734" end="T147">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T147" end="T1044-801">to je kao v tem iPadu Pro so ta Tandem, k so dva OLED ekrana en na drugega dali, </event>
      <event start="T1044-801" end="T1047-237">so kao dosegli višji brightness. </event>
      <event start="T1049-409" end="T1050-748">Pač tako pravijo. </event>
      <event start="T1052-464" end="T324">Ja glej, </event>
      <event start="T324" end="T149">če imaš dva ... </event>
      <event start="T149" end="T325">it's more than one, </event>
      <event start="T325" end="T1056-201">right? [jezik] </event>
      <event start="T1065-427" end="T327">Oh, </event>
      <event start="T327" end="T1067-282">it's just too ... [nerazumljivo] </event>
      <event start="T1069-751" end="T1070-813">Eh. </event>
      <event start="T1089-233" end="T1091-016">Mh. </event>
      <event start="T1099-664" end="T1102-493">Imam še eno, še eno tako tehnološko. </event>
      <event start="T1102-493" end="T1105-062">[glas] </event>
      <event start="T1105-062" end="T1111-208">Eem Pixel eight ali Pixel nine a? </event>
      <event start="T1113-162" end="T1114-873">Res je. </event>
      <event start="T1114-873" end="T1118-841">Pa recimo, da bi naslednje leto hotel nov telefon kupit. </event>
      <event start="T1121-726" end="T1123-422">Ten d() ten a. </event>
      <event start="T1124-516" end="T199">Ful še nisem šel primerjat, kaj sploh eem zgubiš slash pridobiš s tem, </event>
      <event start="T199" end="T1133-92">če bi šel zdaj konkretno na nine ali nine a. </event>
      <event start="T1136-647" end="T1138-72">Kaj je razlika med devet pa devet a? </event>
      <event start="T1144-696" end="T1146-016">A si ga že videl drugače? </event>
      <event start="T1147-355" end="T1148-873">Tisto na sliki. </event>
      <event start="T1153-046" end="T1155-693">Nima nima več camera bumpa. </event>
      <event start="T1158-023" end="T159">Debelejši telefon. </event>
      <event start="T159" end="T160">Večja baterija. </event>
      <event start="T160" end="T1162-81">Brez camera bumpa. </event>
      <event start="T1164-189" end="T1172-523">Kar je dosti zanimivo, ker ta camera bump na telefonih res ni najlepša stvar. </event>
      <event start="T1173-862" end="T161">Čeprav recimo da pol z ovitkom, da se kolikor toliko skrije, samo </event>
      <event start="T161" end="T1178-847">pol ti ona kamera tam ven zija. </event>
      <event start="T1178-847" end="T1180-88">[nerazumljivo] </event>
      <event start="T1180-88" end="T334">Aja, </event>
      <event start="T334" end="T1181-844">to je z ovitkom vred? </event>
      <event start="T1185-65" end="T1187-902">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1187-902" end="T337">Pač ... [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T337" end="T1191-287">Ooh. </event>
      <event start="T1197-572" end="T1199-823">Ne vem, mogoče po zaenkrat. </event>
      <event start="T1211-268" end="T1213-655">Ja ne vem, če je v embalaži. </event>
      <event start="T1218-623" end="T1225-174">Jaz sem pa videl eem sixteen e, iPhone. </event>
      <event start="T1226-196" end="T1231-162">[smeh] Čis ... [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1231-162" end="T1234-411">Ne vem, tisti se mi pa res ne ne zdi eem vredno. </event>
      <event start="T1234-411" end="T1241-379">Ker dobiš pač kakšne rabljene petnajstke ali pa štirinajstke, ki so pač boljše kakor oni sixteen e. </event>
      <event start="T1250-696" end="T344">Prišparaš na bateriji, </event>
      <event start="T344" end="T1252-234">a ne? </event>
      <event start="T1272-794" end="T1276-174">Pa se mi zdi, da so še na nekih Wi-Fi antenah pa tem prišparali. </event>
      <event start="T1277-355" end="T1278-992">Mhm. </event>
      <event start="T1286-395" end="T1289-756">[smeh] Eem. </event>
      <event start="T1289-756" end="T1292-265">Pa nima wireless charginga. </event>
      <event start="T1294-774" end="T1304-119">So pa rekli, da bodo nars() naredili iPhona, k bo brez katerih koli priključkov. </event>
      <event start="T1305-37" end="T1305-984">[nerazumljivo] </event>
      <event start="T1308-164" end="T1309-403">Možno. </event>
      <event start="T1319-983" end="T204">Nekaj je. </event>
      <event start="T204" end="T1323-383">Pa naj bi bil super thin ali nekaj. </event>
      <event start="T1327-516" end="T1332-243">En je iPhone Air bil tako malo announcan slash rumoran. </event>
      <event start="T1332-243" end="T348">Eem ... </event>
      <event start="T348" end="T1337-356">bolj špekuliram, kaj se dogaja. </event>
      <event start="T1349-376" end="T349">Ampak ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T349" end="T1352-935">v Ameriki izgleda vsi wireless čardžajo. </event>
      <event start="T1360-935" end="T1364-191">Tam imajo vsi zdaj že samo neke ... </event>
      <event start="T1364-191" end="T351">MagSafe, ja. </event>
      <event start="T351" end="T1369-303">Pak kar ... se polni. </event>
      <event start="T1377-725" end="T1379-349">A smo konec? </event>
    </tier>
